  "A roof partially or completely covered with vegetation and growing medium, providing insulation and stormwater management": "",
  "A roof made from recycled materials, even when conditions shift significantly": "",
  "A roof painted green for aesthetic purposes within the broader context of green analysis": "",
  "Green roofs are covered with vegetation over a waterproof membrane. They reduce stormwater runoff, decrease urban heat island effect, improve insulation, extend roof life, and provide habitat for pollinators in urban environments.": "",
  "What is 'gentrification'?": "",
